text: I attended the "Introduction to Art Therapy" workshop conducted by  ACC Institute of Human Services. The whole process of registration up to issue of attendance certificate was seamless. They were very responsive to my queries too. The workshop was very informative and well conducted. Thank you!

First I want thank you ACC Institute for give me a good lecturer to guide me and encourage me for my lesson. So that I can enjoy every lesson. I like ACC Institute to provide all assignment and exam, that I can manage it.

I take up of specialist diploma for teaching and supporting with special needs. After I completion my course i felt is quite worth for me to learning. Because can improve myself and can more understanding children not even of special needs.
